snippet.title: Log Jammers - The Legend of Zombear (Trailer)
snippet.description:
ZombieJack and Zombear have a bloody rivalry and the upcoming Log Jam is a chance for them to settle the feud, once and for all.

About Log Jammers:
Don your flannel! Log Jammers is a competitive online/couch arcade game with blazing-fast ax-throwing action. Outwit your opponent, defend your goal, and block your opponent’s throws to win the Log Jam.

Now available on Steam Early Access! Get it here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/684800/Log_Jammers/

For more on Mega Cat Studios and our games, please visit: https://megacatstudios.com/

Come play & talk on discord! www.discord.gg/megacat
